Steps to configure database(windows):

Download the h2.zip file and extract it

move to directory <your_sytem_Path>/h2/bin

execute h2.bat file

for linux h2.sh

It will open h2 console in browser

change only JDBC URL to "jdbc:h2:tcp://localhost/~/bytewheels" from default values displayed

connect to database by pressing connect

Once dtabase is connected 

Type this command to restore backup(bytewheels.sql file is attached)

RUNSCRIPT FROM bytewheels.sql 

NOTE:provide full path for bytewheel.sql for ex: D:\bytewheels.sql

and press run

database is configured now. 






